---
title: Satay Aubergine with Roasted Broccoli and Rice
description: We love a good Satay Aubergine and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/satay-aubergine-c562caed-3f7fa77e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/satay-aubergine-5fbfd4022261465f6165e1d2-8715a4ec.pdf
cuisine: Asian
